tion/opensearchdescription+xml\" href=\"/opensearch_desc.php\" title=\"NetHackWiki\"/>\n<link rel=\"EditURI\" type=\"application/rsd+xml\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/api.php?action=rsd\"/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"/wiki/Sniper_rifle\"/>\n<!--[if lt IE 9]><script src=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=html5shiv&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector&amp;sync=1\"></script><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Sniper_rifle rootpage-Sniper_rifle skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Sniper rifle</h1>\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From NetHackWiki</div>\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\"></div>\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#p-search\">Jump to search</a>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"margin: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-cyan\">)</span> <a href=\"/wiki/File:Sniper_rifle.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Sniper rifle.png\" src=\"/images/3/35/Sniper_rifle.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<td>sniper rifle\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Appearance\n</th>\n<td>sniper rifle\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Damage vs. small\n</th>\n<td>1d2\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Damage vs. large\n</th>\n<td>1d2\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>To-hit bonus\n</th>\n<td>+4\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Weapon skill\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Firearms\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Firearms\">firearms</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Size\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Two-handed\" title=\"Two-handed\">two-handed</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Base price\n</th>\n<td>4000 <a href=\"/wiki/Zorkmid\" title=\"Zorkmid\">zm</a><br />(+10/positive <br />enchant)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Weight\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Weight\" title=\"Weight\">50</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Material\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Iron\" title=\"Iron\">iron</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p>A sniper rifle is a <a href=\"/wiki/Firearm\" title=\"Firearm\">firearm</a> introduced in <a href=\"/wiki/SLASH%27EM\" title=\"SLASH&#39;EM\">SLASH'EM</a>. It is very accurate (+4) and long-ranged (25), but its low rate of fire makes <a href=\"/wiki/Multishot\" title=\"Multishot\">multishots</a> impossible without <a href=\"/wiki/Overenchant\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Overenchant\">overenchanting</a>.  It is <a href=\"/wiki/Two-handed\" title=\"Two-handed\">two-handed</a> and fires <a href=\"/wiki/Bullet\" title=\"Bullet\">bullets</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Rate_of_fire\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Rate of fire</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Generation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Generation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Strategy\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Strategy</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Origin\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Origin</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Rate_of_fire\">Rate of fire</span></h2>\n<table class=\"prettytable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Enchantment\n</th>\n<th>Unskilled/basic\n</th>\n<th>Skilled\n</th>\n<th>Expert\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>+8 or lower\n</td>\n<td>1\n</td>\n<td>1\n</td>\n<td>1\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>+9\n</td>\n<td>1\n</td>\n<td>1\n</td>\n<td>1d6-4 (min 1)\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Generation\">Generation</span></h2>\n<p>Sniper rifles are not randomly generated.\n</p><p>There is a <sup>2</sup>&#8260;<sub>5</sub> chance of one of the <a href=\"/wiki/Soldier\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Soldier\">soldiers</a> in <a href=\"/wiki/Grund%27s_Stronghold\" title=\"Grund&#39;s Stronghold\">Grund's Stronghold</a> generating with a +3 sniper rifle.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Strategy\">Strategy</span></h2>\n<p>While very accurate, the sniper rifle's low rate of fire and two-handedness make it nearly useless.  It does have a higher monetary value than any other firearm at 4000zm, but by the time one reaches Grund's Stronghold, that amount of gold is not likely to be significant.  While the sniper rifle does have a longer range than any other firearm, this is unlikely to be factor in most games, since it is rare to be firing at targets halfway across the map.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Origin\">Origin</span></h2>\n<p>Sniper rifles are specialized weapons designed to be accurate at extremely long ranges in the hands of a skilled sharpshooter.  Some sniper rifles are derived from ordinary service weapons - usually <a href=\"/wiki/Assault_rifle\" title=\"Assault rifle\">assault rifles</a> or semi-automatic <a href=\"/wiki/Rifle\" title=\"Rifle\">rifles</a> - while others are designed from the ground up as specialist weapons.  They usually feature accuracy-focused enhancements such as bipods and large scopes.\n</p>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:44px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"This article may require revision for the next version of SLASH&#39;EM. Click here for more information.\"><img alt=\"This article may require revision for the next version of SLASH&#39;EM. Click here for more information.\" src=\"/images/3/38/Se7e7-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"This article describes a 3.4.3-based variant of NetHack. Click here for more information.\"><img alt=\"This article describes a 3.4.3-based variant of NetHack. Click here for more information.\" src=\"/images/5/5d/Nh343var-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926190458\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.021 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.027 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 235/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1020/1000000\nPost‚Äêexpand include size: 3232/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 667/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‚Äêexpand size: 2/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   13.230      1 -total\n 36.62%    4.845      1 Template:Slashem-7E7\n 35.03%    4.635      2 Template:Version_icon\n 34.23%    4.529      1 Template:Weapon\n 23.70%    3.135      2 Template:Top_icon\n 18.52%    2.450      1 Template:Metal_color\n 17.00%    2.249      1 Template:Variant-343\n 10.22%    1.352      1 Template:Frac\n  8.81%    1.166      1 Template:Cyan\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wikihackdb:pcache:idhash:15251-0!canonical and timestamp 20240926190458 and revision id 175259\n -->\n</div></div>\t\t\t\t\